{"tid":1279941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人不要再分化 一齊邁向目標","createTime":"2019-07-02T20:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T02:51:53.000Z","uid":31311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ea8442997647afd801ae3e438fbebdee51a054","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:48:34.000Z","msg":"不論和理非非<br />\n不論勇武派<br />\n不論鍵盤戰士都好<br />\n請求大家不要再分化<br />\n我地香港人黎架！一齊守衛我地嘅地方好冇啊？<br />\n政府繼續龜縮，我哋就要更加堅強<br />\n呢一場係持久戰<br />\n可能大家會覺得攰 會覺得無力<br />\n但係點都好 仲有香港人去撐住<br />\n一個都不能少 <br />\n當我求下大家 我知道大家為香港付出左好多嘢<br />\n但係大家千其唔好心灰意冷<br />\n因為我哋呢一場運動係需要長時間抗爭<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45054559d536f2266af6d0799b545ff07f7856cf","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e062ded81151864fc5ee0638c265a0eaf047df0b","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:49:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db2ac14dd3037fbf041ba1d614a09a6b05c2339a","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2142a85afb428576fa7665641927b8b51cb83a4","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b84292789c90ec9f549c187eaf1c42489e5d7de1","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:50:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e9d5d03c8cc0136d0fb2c550d207d9f5d80dca7","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34d12f5d57799ab5d9cdaa78eaeda343da72fd4a","tid":1279941,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc